Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.13,0:00:05.84,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{Prodotto Società per azioni FMS efu emu sapurai (fornitura)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.32,0:01:51.03,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.62,0:01:54.56,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.53,0:01:57.50,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Hey Mom, I will walk with Momoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.72,0:01:58.62,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.00,0:01:59.93,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Instead of a walk
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:01.71,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,better think about how to get into a good school
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.75,0:02:03.47,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,is a good institution and a good company.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.32,0:02:06.34,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Again began.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.49,0:02:07.68,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Nothing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.79,0:02:08.65,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Listen to me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.71,0:02:11.86,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,if you will be lazy when you grow up, you will become like your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.16,0:02:15.47,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Then in Kyushu, then in Hokkaido, wears it all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.35,0:02:19.27,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,So start your studies. Be diligent, Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.22,0:02:21.05,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Sì...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.74,0:02:34.09,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,It's your fault, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.38,0:02:36.86,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,As soon as Takeshi was born, you immediately left for Hokkaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.19,0:02:38.66,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,And since then everything is on the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.73,0:02:40.58,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Then Tohoku, then Shikoku, then Kyushu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.99,0:02:42.82,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,And everywhere alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.94,0:02:45.51,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,So you have no time left for raising a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.37,0:02:47.68,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,I really...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.07,0:02:49.97,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,feel lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.44,0:03:10.93,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Do me a favor ...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.51,0:03:13.14,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,woman's friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.63,0:04:03.13,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,No! Need to learn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.44,0:04:04.16,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Learn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.17,0:04:07.16,Internal,,0,0,0,,Le... arn...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.71,0:04:23.10,Flashback,,0,0,0,,No! Do not!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:52.01,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.68,0:04:54.21,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,This is from the laundry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.47,0:04:56.50,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Will there be an order today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.12,0:04:57.78,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.93,0:05:00.10,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,This voice. Ken-chan from the laundry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.77,0:05:01.44,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Allora..?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.05,0:05:02.98,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.54,0:05:06.96,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.68,0:05:13.30,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Takeshi! Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.09,0:05:16.90,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.60,0:05:22.78,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're still studying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.28,0:05:25.41,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,It is harmful to do so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:27.22,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,From time to time you have to go for a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.79,0:05:28.38,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.06,0:05:31.37,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Now you'll be busy preparing for exams all the time, will not you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:33.85,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,And now you have the opportunity to walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.02,0:05:36.54,Dialogo,,0,0,0,, But, mom, you have just ...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.86,0:05:37.51,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.61,0:05:40.30,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Momoe also wants to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.92,0:05:43.21,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Quickly, go out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.85,0:05:44.82,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.02,0:05:57.08,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Well, here we are at the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.23,0:05:58.54,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{Eh?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.69,0:06:01.55,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,, In the afternoon \Nthere is no place to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.90,0:06:03.79,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,After all...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.92,0:06:05.90,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,There is no such hidden place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.73,0:06:09.46,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,What's the matter? \N What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.13,0:06:10.60,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:11.83,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Go here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.34,0:06:14.02,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,But, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.24,0:06:40.31,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.73,0:06:47.29,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,That's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.95,0:06:50.41,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,No! Someone is watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.48,0:06:51.36,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.29,0:06:53.66,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,It's true! Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.31,0:06:55.01,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.06,0:07:05.06,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,I'm all wet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.12,0:07:06.42,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Momoe, it's your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.67,0:07:08.70,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,It would have be better\N if you had warned me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.06,0:07:10.58,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Eh? Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.57,0:07:12.82,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,You saw something at the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.88,0:07:13.81,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.30,0:07:26.91,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Momoe, nice job!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.29,0:07:39.58,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Already developed? {not so clear the meaning}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.98,0:07:44.62,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Next is..?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.46,0:07:51.09,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.82,0:07:54.67,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,What? Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.00,0:07:55.61,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.24,0:08:08.56,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,What a beauty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.99,0:08:11.70,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.21,0:08:21.74,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.16,0:08:40.46,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{Ehh...}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.97,0:08:42.43,Internal,,0,0,0,,What a beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.28,0:08:44.04,Internal,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.33,0:08:45.84,Internal,,0,0,0,,such a cutie...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:47.61,Internal,,0,0,0,,it would be nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.01,0:08:58.08,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Momoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.00,0:10:04.61,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.27,0:10:05.92,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Your lips... 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.78,0:10:17.79,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Ken-Chan, are you already tired? {Yoreyore - sgualcito, sfilacciato, consumato, stanco.}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.83,0:10:19.70,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Now open your legs, madam. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:23.06,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,My business... the laundry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:26.43,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,More.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:29.35,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.36,0:10:44.92,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.19,0:10:48.54,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Ikuyo, it's me, Tatsuzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.60,0:10:49.99,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.62,0:10:53.61,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Takeshi diligently engaged?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.60,0:10:57.31,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Ah... Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.36,0:10:57.69,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.77,0:10:58.63,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Everything is alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.45,0:11:03.17,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,The mood for studying at Takeshi... is very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.29,0:11:04.25,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{Oh, bene}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.49,0:11:05.14,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.20,0:11:06.75,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Are you calm now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.71,0:11:08.96,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Bene.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.29,0:11:13.95,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,I'm working with him now... with enthusiasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.01,0:11:15.68,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.02,0:11:22.22,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Whit this attitude...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.59,0:11:25.07,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,I'll also work with enthusiasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:28.46,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Good mood... good... good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.61,0:11:30.29,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Sì, good mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.53,0:11:32.61,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Then, I will finish soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.87,0:11:35.45,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Well, try there. \N I will try too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:38.65,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Yes dear, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:42.50,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Well, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.55,0:12:00.15,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.51,0:12:05.16,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,This is not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.49,0:12:08.99,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's no good...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:10.46,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Our family is falling apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.78,0:12:14.57,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,But Mom was so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.34,0:12:18.74,Internal,,0,0,0,,I also want to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.17,0:12:32.72,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,If desire could somehow help...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.98,0:13:28.17,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Tomokatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.85,0:13:30.03,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Tomokatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.23,0:13:37.85,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Tomokatsu, where did you run to? What a mischievous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.76,0:13:41.74,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Oh, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.83,0:13:43.57,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.67,0:13:57.22,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Enough, Momoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.04,0:14:00.18,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,You can't meet him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.50,0:14:12.52,Dialogo,,0,0,0,, Why did you bring me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.63,0:14:14.70,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Eh? You want go in?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.86,0:14:16.70,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,It's impossible.\N I will look like a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:20.07,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,I understood. If I come in, will you calm down?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.15,0:14:34.02,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Understood. I need to peek in?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.44,0:14:46.31,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,That girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.92,0:15:13.79,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Still can not. Be patient a little more, Tomokatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.97,0:15:29.23,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Now you can, Tomokatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.58,0:15:30.16,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.62,0:16:03.56,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Why am I not in the \Nplace of that dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.69,0:16:26.91,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Tomokatsu,  what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.82,0:16:28.24,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Tomok...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.18,0:16:35.33,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Tomokatsu, you..!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.59,0:16:41.45,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Momoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.20,0:16:43.15,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Now you can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.86,0:16:46.20,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,But ... it looks nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.48,0:16:49.43,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Momoe...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.23,0:16:59.01,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,H-Hello! I-I am Takeshi, the master of Momoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:02.37,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,And I am Sayuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:07.32,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Sayuri-san, I'm sorry. At times lei... {Qui, piuttosto,??????? - Koitsu a kitara - (scusa, quello) è venuto con lei - una continuazione della frase precedente}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:08.86,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Takeshi-san, everything is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.38,0:17:17.12,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Takeshi-san, let's do it us too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.36,0:17:18.15,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.65,0:17:20.08,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.59,0:17:21.85,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,With pleasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.78,0:17:28.65,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Sayuri-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.84,0:17:33.19,Internal,,0,0,0,,Sayuri-san!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.55,0:17:34.83,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Takeshi-san!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.44,0:18:47.37,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Her it is!
